forcebindip (1.0.0) stable; urgency=low

  * Initial release of ForceBindIP for Linux
  * Cross-platform network interface binding tool
  * IPv4 and IPv6 support
  * Interface binding by name or IP address
  * TCP and UDP socket binding support
  * LD_PRELOAD implementation for Linux
  * Verbose logging and debugging features
  * Support for VPN routing and multi-network setups
  * Compatible with major applications (browsers, CLI tools, etc.)
  * Complete Persian and English documentation

